    "Of course, the first step for the applicability of this method is the availability of the data, meaning that the required monitoring observations for periods of years should have been scheduled and taken place, a demanding and expensive task.",
    "LSST will dramatically improve on the availability of microlensing light curves by monitoring thousands of lensed quasars for at least a decade.",
    "However, the potential advantages of the light curve method come at the cost of complicated calculations, additional model degeneracies, and some \"hidden\" complexity in the data.",
